          <img class="sec-img inf-img" src={IMG + "verify-hand-raised-breeder-60-seconds.webp"} srcset={IMG + "verify-hand-raised-breeder-60-seconds-760.webp 760w, " + IMG + "verify-hand-raised-breeder-60-seconds.webp 1408w"} sizes="(max-width:900px) 92vw, 760px" width="1408" height="768" loading="lazy" alt="Three fast checks to verify a legitimate hand-raised African Grey breeder: ask for the USDA license, video-call the bird live, reverse-image the photos" />
