          <img class="sec-img inf-img" src={IMG + "hand-raised-grey-shipping-tiers.webp"} srcset={IMG + "hand-raised-grey-shipping-tiers-760.webp 760w, " + IMG + "hand-raised-grey-shipping-tiers.webp 1408w"} sizes="(max-width:900px) 92vw, 760px" width="1408" height="768" loading="lazy" alt="Getting your hand-raised grey home safely: airport pickup $185, home delivery $350, or Midland pickup within 2 to 3 hours, via IATA live-animal cargo on Delta, United and American" />
          <h3>Airport pickup and home delivery, explained</h3>
          <p>Airport pickup at $185 puts your grey on a direct flight to your nearest major cargo airport; home delivery at $350 brings it door-to-door. Both routes carry the full document folder and health certificate with the bird.</p>
          <h4>Which airlines and travel crates do we use?</h4>
