          <p>Yes — buyers who live a couple of hours out often just drive in and collect their bird by hand, which skips shipping entirely and gives the grey the calmest possible start. We genuinely love meeting the families our birds go home with, so if reaching Midland, Texas is realistic for you, tell us. Shipping to nearby states is easy too — <a href="/african-grey-parrot-for-sale-texas/">start with our Texas hand-raised greys page</a> if you're local.</p>
