        <div class="seam-wrap" role="presentation"><img class="seam" src={seam} alt="" loading="lazy" width="182" height="60" /></div>

        <!-- ===== 17 · RESOURCES ===== -->
        <section id="resources" class="sec">
          <h2>Keep reading before you choose a hand-raised grey</h2>
          <p class="opener">A hand-raised grey is a 40-year decision, so read a little further before you reserve — these guides answer the questions this page only touched. Each one is written the same first-person way, by the people who actually raise the birds.</p>
