              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="seam-wrap" role="presentation"><img class="seam" src={seam} alt="" loading="lazy" width="182" height="60" /></div>

        <!-- ===== 18 · RESERVE ===== -->
        <section id="reserve" class="sec">
          <h2>Reserve your hand-raised African Grey today</h2>
          <p class="opener">Ready to bring one home? Tell us which grey caught your eye and how you'd like it delivered, and Teri will reply personally within 24 hours — no bots, no pressure. A {deposit} refundable deposit holds your bird while we arrange the details.</p>
          <div class="cta-form">
            <div class="form-side">
              <h3>Tell us which bird is yours</h3>
              <p>Every grey below is hand-raised, documented and available now. Pick one — or ask us to help you choose between a Congo and a Timneh.</p>
